MMM Savings Rate (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added Beeware/Toga GUI application with tabbed interface
  * Full configuration editing with form validation and persistence
  * Read-only income and savings data viewing with spreadsheet integration
  * Shared TinyDB configuration between CLI and GUI applications
  * Cross-platform spreadsheet editing integration (Windows/macOS/Linux)
  * Console script entry point for savingsrates-gui command
  * Briefcase packaging for .deb distribution
  * Project restructured to src/ layout for better packaging
  * GUI and CLI coexistence - both interfaces work independently with shared config
  * New GUI tests
  * Switched to pytest and briefcase for testing
  * Console scripts: savingsrates, sr-show-config, sr-validate-config, sr-update-setting
  * Added automatic file watching for GUI - plots refresh automatically when spreadsheets are saved
  * Automatic plot refresh when configuration is saved in GUI
  * Python watchdog integration with threading for seamless user experience
  * 1-second debouncing to prevent excessive refreshes during rapid file saves
  * Improved UX: moved manual refresh button from plot tab to config tab and application menu

 -- Brad Busenius <bbusenius@gmail.com>  Sat, 26 Jul 2025 01:30:00 +0000

MMM Savings Rate (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * New TinyDB JSON config format
  * Removed INI files and dependencies
  * Fixed Bokeh circle glyph deprecation warning
  * Updated documentation theme to sphinx_rtd_theme
  * Added Read the Docs configuration
  * Add --output CLI argument for specifying HTML file location
  * Update documentation with pandoc prerequisite

